The search pipeline found the right chunks — CodeParser class, CodeChunk, and even a TypeScript test file. GPT-4o just needs a real API key in `.env`.

## To make it work with a real API key

Edit `.env` and set your actual OpenAI key:
```
LLM_API_KEY=sk-your-real-key-here
```

Then restart the server and query again.

